Can’t believe it’s been a year already.. time really does fly! Reminiscing all the fun memories,countless hours of designing each look, the trials, the rehearsal and finally seeing it all come alive!

Collaborating with such a talented team to bring this vision to life was an absolute joy. My heartfelt gratitude to every individual who contributed their efforts and talents, you’ve left an indelible mark on this experience. Here’s to cherished memories and the magic of creativity that binds us all together 💕✨

Happy brides are the prettiest 🥰 

Had an amazing time getting @aparnanadig ready for her dream wedding! We opted for soft glam makeup to accentuate her natural beauty and create a look that’s both timeless and stunning. 

The goal was to enhance her features without overshadowing her radiant smile and joy. So grateful to be a part of her special day and witness her happiness!
